meanings.english_definition: A female given name, likely a variant of Carolyn or Karen.

etymology.value: Likely a modern variant or combination of the names Karen, Carolyn, or similar names.

usage_notes.explanation: Karylin is a relatively uncommon given name. It is often perceived as a modern or creative variation of more traditional names.

readability_explanation.text: The name Karylin is easy to pronounce and recognize. It is similar to other common names.
